#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:1
msgid "vtkCell Triangulate function refactoring"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:3
msgid "Motivations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:5
msgid ""
"Triangulate function returns both the point ids and point coordinates of the "
"cells. But most of the time, when this is called, only the ids are used."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:7
msgid ""
"Avoiding to return point coordinates would remove some unnecessary "
"allocations and point copies. But the most important gains are for Bezier "
"cells where nodes are not interpolatory, and so returning the points involve "
"multiple basis evaluations. Thanks to that, vtkDataSetSurfaceFilter is much "
"faster with Bezier cells, and we can see the effects when rendering in "
"Paraview."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:11
msgid "Implementations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:13
msgid "Now, in the vtkCell interfaces, there are three functions:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:14
msgid ""
"Triangulate( ids, points ): Existing function that returns the triangulated "
"points and global ids (function not deprecated)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:15
msgid ""
"TriangulateIds( ids ): New function that only returns the triangulated "
"global ids"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:16
msgid ""
"TriangulateLocalIds( ids ): New function that only returns the triangulated "
"local ids. Before, Triangulate was implemented for each cell type. Now "
"Triangulate is only implemented in the source code of vtkCell, and it is "
"TriangulateLocalIds that is implemented for each cell type. Triangulate and "
"TriangulateIds are both called TriangulateLocalIds in the source code of "
"vtkCell."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:21
msgid "Minor additional changes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:23
msgid "Fix a bug in vtkQuadraticPolygon::PermuteFromPolygon"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:24
msgid "Slightly speed up vtkDataSetSurfaceFilter for nonlinear cells."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:25
msgid "Slightly speed up vtkPolygon::BoundedTriangulate"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:26
msgid "Remove a lot of DeepCopy in vtkPolygon"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/refactor-vtkCell-triangulate.md:27
msgid ""
"Deprecate vtkPolygon::Triangulate and vtkQuadraticPolygon::Triangulate "
"function."
msgstr ""
